			[NOTORIETY DECREASED X2 - UNION]
			
			[NOTORIETY DECREASED - HARMONY]
			
			[NOTORIETY DECREASED - MINISTRY]
			
			[NOTORIETY DECREASED - GATHERING]
			
			[NOTORIETY DECREASED - FREE MANTIS]
			
			[NOTORIETY DECREASED - GENIOCRACY]
			
