<textList name="EG_CIVILIAN_RESOURCES_TEXT">
	<text>Another peacefully-minded ship flies past you. You explain to it that you're slightly short on resources, and it agrees to help you out a bit.</text>
	<text>You contact the passing ship. Its captain accepts the call, and you explain to it that you're slightly short on resources. They agree to help you a bit.</text>
	<text>Out of the kindness of its heart, the passing ship decides to give you some resources after learning that you're planning to crush the Rebellion in this universe.</text>
</textList>

<textList name="EG_CIVILIAN_BARTER_TEXT">
	<text>A ship damaged by pirates flies near you. You contact it and offer a barter.</text>
	<text>Other civilians fly past you. They are short of certain resources and agree to barter.</text>
	<text>A ship contacts you and offers a barter before you do.</text>
</textList>

<textList name="EG_CIVILIAN_SHOP_TEXT">
	<text>You're looking for a store in the area and finally find one. Its owner is happy to see new customers.</text>
	<text>Not far from this beacon, you find a small mobile trading station. You dock with it without any problems.</text>
	<text>There's an outpost on the nearest planet. Its inhabitants agree to trade with you.</text>
</textList>
<textList name="EG_CIVILIAN_SHOP_REPAIR_TEXT">
	<text>You're looking for a store in the area and finally find one. Its owner is happy to see new customers and is even willing to provide you with free repairs at the business's expense.</text>
	<text>Not far from this beacon, you find a small mobile trading station. As one of its visitors, they've decided to offer you a small, free repair.</text>
	<text>There's an outpost on the nearest planet. Its inhabitants agree to trade with you and provide free repairs.</text>
</textList>

<event name="EG_CIVILIAN_ASTEROIDS">
	<text>You've explored the surrounding area to no avail and stumbled into an asteroid field. It seems luck is not on your side.</text>
	<variable name="eg_second_voice_req" op="set" val="0"/>
	<environment type="asteroid"/>
	<modifyPursuit amount="1"/>
	<choice>
		<text>Continue...</text>
		<event/>
	</choice>
</event>


